data.description: This charming 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem boasts a bonus room and a 2-story layout. Inside, discover the warmth of hardwood and vinyl plank flooring on the first level. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, stunning blue cabinets with gold hardware—a modern touch that elevates the entire space. Step outside to a spacious fully fenced backyard, offering ultimate privacy. Entertain guests on the large wooden deck or gather around the fire pit for cozy evenings. This home is an entertainer's paradise—your perfect haven awaits!
